PROVINCE OF MANITOBA  –  GOVERNMENT INFESTED WITH SUBVERSIVE ANTI-PESTICIDE LUNATICS


 

 
 
 
The Government of Manitoba is INFESTED
 
WITH SUBVERSIVE ANTI-PESTICIDE LUNATICS

 
 
 
Ontario's Lunatic-Vermin Have Been
 
Let Out Of Their Cages To Help
 
The Government DESTROY Manitoba's
 
Professional Lawn Care Industry
 
 
 
The Government of Manitoba will,
 
BEYOND ANY DOUBT, TRY TO
 
IMPOSE ANTI-PESTICIDE PROHIBITION
 
 
 
THE VERMIN OF ANTI-PESTICIDE
 
TERRORISM MUST BE STOPPED !
 
 
 
STOP PROHIBITION in Manitoba
 
to stop it NATIONALLY !
 
 
 
RESPOND TO THE ON-LINE
 
CONSULTATION  …  SEVERAL TIMES !
 
 
 
Anyone from the Green Space Industry
 
who DOES NOT complete Manitoba’s
 
ON-LINE CONSULTATION is a PITIFUL FOOL
 
and an IDIOT, and DOES NOT DESERVE
 
a career, or a business, or any success
 
in the Green Space Industry
 
 
 
 
 
Manitoba Conspiracy To Prohibit Pest Control Products
 
 
The Government of Manitoba is INFESTED WITH SUBVERSIVE ANTI-PESTICIDE LUNATIC-TERRORISTS.
 
The Government of Manitoba WANTS ANTI-PESTICIDE PROHIBITION.
 
Conversely, the VAST SILENT MAJORITY of the population DOES NOT WANT PROHIBITION, particularly those who work in the Professional Lawn Care Industry.
 
With PROHIBITION, Manitoba’s Green Spaces will become GARBAGE DUMPS.
 
 
