Province of Manitoba Canada: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback


































province of manitoba canada
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Government
Industry: Government Regional
Sub-Industry: -
Province of Manitoba Canada is a province in South Central Canada. The Province is bordered by the provinces of Ontario to the east, Saskatchewan to the west, Nunavut and Northwest Territories to the north, and United States to the south. The Province of Manitoba economy is primarily based on manufacturing, mining, agriculture, and forestry.




Corporate Information
Address:

204 Legislative Building
450 Broadway
Winnipeg, MB R3C 0V8
Canada


Phone:
1-204-945-3714


Fax:
1-204-949-1484


