Partnership Agreement






          Contact Information
         



          The only contact information we need is your e-mail address. It allows us to send you the
          finished documents. It will not be included in the documents.
         




E-mail:





Names of Partners and Partnership Shares
         



          Enter the full names of all partners (up to 5 may be entered) with their respective Partnership 
          Shares in the fields beside their names.  Please enter the shares such that each partner has the
          correct fraction of the total.

          Example 1: If the partners are equal partners, give them each the same number of shares.  In this
          case there is no effective difference between giving each partner one share, or ten shares.

          Example 2: If you wish to assign shares as a straightforward percentage, make sure the total shares
          adds up to 100.  This can be difficult to do in some situations, like when there are three equal partners.
         





